The paper discusses the development and evaluation of a distributed intrusion detection system for SCADA systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the use of ensemble methods and social network metrics for improving the accuracy of the intrusion detection system, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), social and information networks (cs.SI), and software engineering (cs.SE).
